{"tid":1529020,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉場攻略］唔想再有人走唔切嘅入嚟","createTime":"2019-09-01T15:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T17:45:24.000Z","uid":239080,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"df342f4142a713ca71b1685c50b372a7ad8500d2","tid":1529020,"uid":239080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">［企法］</span></strong></ins><br />\n喺同狗隻對峙嘅時候 大家可以企鬆啲 人同人之間有一至兩<span style=\"color: red;\">個手位</span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ufjTgS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ufjTgS.jpg&h=665f89ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時就算企鬆咗 但係好多人<span style=\"color: red;\">一後退又逼返埋一齊</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzddic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzddic.jpg&h=5e94f6ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以就算退後咗都好<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">聽到停</span>嘅時候都唔好9秒9企定定喺到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">行後啲 企鬆啲先</span><br />\n<br />\n有時可能聽到有人大叫企鬆啲 但係你覺得自己己經企得好鬆喎<br />\n咁可能係下圖咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCV0CNg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCV0CNg.jpg&h=55e05184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇嘢做嘅可以行個大圈先<br />\n睇下會唔會一<span style=\"color: red;\">跑嘅時候比後面塞死</span><br />\n會嘅唔該<span style=\"color: red;\">自己叫人</span>企鬆啲<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">［後退］</span></strong></ins><br />\n向後走緊嘅時候 希望可以<span style=\"color: red;\">保持返本身個距離</span><br />\n而前線一定係第一個後退嘅人嚟<br />\n較後嘅人一定係遲過佢起步 慢過佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XNLPwg3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXNLPwg3.jpg&h=6c85fd2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以要行得<span style=\"color: red;\">快過前線小小</span> 以免逼到上嚟走唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PMxm6QY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPMxm6QY.jpg&h=7bbfed02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係記得唔好走太快 總之<span style=\"color: red;\">要留有足夠空間</span><br />\n<br />\n行緊嘅時候 各位手足<span style=\"color: red;\">望住前線</span>嗰面 倒後行 <br />\n隻手<span style=\"color: red;\">捉住身邊手足</span> 建議捉書包 唔好落單<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有咩事一齊衝返去前面救人</span><br />\n<br />\n到跑嘅時候 最好向返後望 可以跑快啲<br />\n但係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記得記得望返去前線</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有事返去救人</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>高階跑法<br />\n有練開波嘅 可以試下做footwork咁跑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">［ROADBLOCK］</span></ins></em></em></strong><br />\n留守得耐 啲狗一定會包抄 一定要封晒啲橫街 <br />\n搵哨兵睇水 最好有walkie talkie組成一個網<br />\n哨兵提醒前線有人包抄<br />\n喺前線落到嚟之前搵人頂住啲狗<br />\n唔好比佢哋衝入嚟包抄<br />\n其他唔係幫手頂住嘅人繼續行 唔好阻住前線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fcccb9ee48ce8fc2401fe3ff99ebde08112f3b","tid":1529020,"uid":239080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:59:11.000Z","msg":"呢排啲狗中意衝入mtr 封站 去碼頭封手足逃生路線 <br />\n走到快啲走 換衫 除gear <br />\n個袋唔好放有個人資料嘅嘢 <br />\n有咩事dump咗個袋佢"},{"pid":"d9baf19bd38d588b131b7ace26d4f46990f8c9b3","tid":1529020,"uid":239080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:59:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"413de40b207c33cfa9e3e8e5c1e4a1672c12eb0c","tid":1529020,"uid":239080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54998d6902910973f9c9640e2ac799374f49ffa9","tid":1529020,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df96c45ce61aff61b4a69f3e50ce37af030717d8","tid":1529020,"uid":239080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s